WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:06.660 --> 00:00:08.220
Excuse me?

00:00:10.620 --> 00:00:13.420
Excuse me. Just a moment, please.

00:00:17.280 --> 00:00:17.820
Sure.

00:00:31.900 --> 00:00:33.900
Thank you for waiting.

00:00:39.480 --> 00:00:41.480
How may I help you?

00:00:45.640 --> 00:00:48.240
I'm Albert, room 501.

00:00:52.240 --> 00:00:54.240
There are a few things I gotta tell you.

00:00:58.620 --> 00:01:01.920
Firstly, the air conditioner doesn't seem to work.

00:01:07.280 --> 00:01:10.740
Secondly, I can't stand the smell of cigarettes.

00:01:16.220 --> 00:01:19.520
Finally, I couldn't get through to the front desk.

00:01:27.460 --> 00:01:29.460
I'm very sorry.

00:01:33.460 --> 00:01:37.100
If you like, I could move you to a different room.

00:01:41.940 --> 00:01:43.520
I'd like to.

00:01:48.620 --> 00:01:52.120
Then, I'll give you the new room key.

00:01:59.800 --> 00:02:01.800
Thank you.

00:02:06.360 --> 00:02:09.720
If you need anything, would you let us know.

